cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SI 

The paper presents a visualisation and analysis system for multidimensional data, which is a common topic in computer graphics (cs.GR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The system also involves querying and organising data, which relates to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses collaboration and discovery in research scenarios, which could fall under social and information sciences (cs.SI).
